<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 5 (Luke) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルーク</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Luke</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ガイ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Guy</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんだ？　消えちまったぞ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the heck? It vanished?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まさか俺達、世界を救ったのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Did we really save the world?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんかよくわかんねぇ奴だったな。
祈りとか願いとか、なんだそりゃ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Such a confusing person.
What's with this whole prayers and wishes thing?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シュヴァルツか。
ルークとの相性は最悪だったみたいだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Schwartz, huh.
Seems like Luke's behavior
was the worst thing for her.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Not sure about this one. 相性 means affniity/compatibility/chemistry. 最悪 means "the worst"/awful/terrible/etc. More literally, Luke's chemistry with Schwartz is bad/the worst possible. Given Guy's following dialogue, he's referring to Luke's selfishness with this, and viewing it as a good thing that they had bad chemistry.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だが今回は、それが世界を救った</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But that saved the world this time.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルークのわがままも
案外バカに出来ないのかもな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Your selfishness surprisingly
might not be so terrible.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あぁ？　なんか言ったか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? You say something?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いや、なんでもない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nah, nothing.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>つうか腹減ったー。
ガイ、さっさと帰ろうぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Anyway, I'm starving.
Guy, let's go home.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、わかってる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, gotcha.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……まったく。　世話の焼ける奴だよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Really, though. He's such a handful.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Unreferenced</Section>
